  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Treatment for Chronic Hepatitis C With Normal Transaminases in HIV Positive Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>CONTRA</acronym>
  <official_title>Open Multicentre, Phase IV Study to Evaluate Efficacy and Safety of Pegylated Interferon Alpha-2a (40 KD) Plus Ribavirin for Chronic Hepatitis C With Normal Transaminases in Human Immunodeficiency Virus-infected Patients</official_title>
